  <features>
    <feature>A very simple yet deep mechanic: piling!</feature>
    <feature>A memorable journey about friendship, helpfulness and never leaving anyone behind!</feature>
	<feature>A drop in / drop out feature allowing players to join and leave at any time thanks to dynamic challenge rescalling!</feature>
    <feature>3 compelling worlds to explore and secrets to unravel!</feature>
    <feature>6 crazy mini-games and their variations to spice things up!</feature>
	<feature>8 new skins to unlock, and many more toys and custom options!</feature>
	<feature>An art direction entirely revolving around cardboard, from textures to sound design!</feature>
  </features>

